thread.title: Lina

author: Lina
title: Lina
text: Selling our house was not only stressful but very emotional. Both Joe and Truc were nothing short of professional in every aspect, constantly providing us with feedback and always providing sound advice. We are 110% happy with not only the result, but also the way in which our campaign was handled. Joe and Truc are a true testament to working for the client; I have no hesitation in recommending Nelson Alexander Preston.
